 1540:                 f"Domain {domain!r} is a peer-reviewed journal but the "
 1541:                 f"title appears truncated (ends with ellipsis). Can't "
 1542:                 f"reliably detect SR/MA/perspective/guideline from a "
 1543:                 f"partial title, so defaulting to T4. Fetch the full "
 1544:                 f"title via OpenAlex display_name or page content to "
 1545:                 f"reclassify."
 1546:             )
 1547:             return result
 1548: 
 1549:         # M-15 guard 2 REVERTED: the blanket "NIH aggregator → T4 when
