 1551:         # primaries (cycle 9: 0 releases / 8 aborts, T1=0% everywhere).
 1552:         # OpenAlex lookups fail often enough that the fallback path
 1553:         # hits NIH content regularly. Keeping truncated-title guard
 1554:         # (guard 1) and society-tool guard (guard 3) which are more
 1555:         # surgical. Codex pass 16 can assess whether remaining NIH
