codex
So far I don’t see a bypass around the tier classifier or an eviction of ordinary search results on the intended `seed_urls=None` and afib seed paths. I found one narrow validation weakness around empty DOI components; I’m running the targeted seed tests before deciding whether that rises above advisory.
